%20on%20the%20stage%20talk%20about%20things%20like%20national%20abortion%20bans%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20governor%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20watched%20eight%20people%20on%20stage%20talking%20about%20how%20much%20they%20would%20want%20to%20cut%20Medicaid%20and%20Social%20Security.%20We%20watched%20eight%20people%20obviously%20say%20that%20law%20and%20order%20doesn't%20matter.%20Because%20convictions%20to%20them%20wouldn't%20matter.%26quot%3B%3Cu%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoore%20then%20said%20that%20when%20he%20travels%20throughout%20Maryland%2C%20the%20issues%20he%20hears%20from%20people%20aren't%20aligned%20with%20what%20the%20GOP%20presidential%20contenders%20offered%20Americans%20this%20week%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20political%20affiliation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20care%20what%20part%20of%20the%20state%20of%20Maryland%20I'm%20going%20to%20%E2%80%94%20in%20Democratic%20areas%20or%20traditionally%20historically%20voting%20Republican%20areas%20%E2%80%94%20what%20they%20were%20saying%20was%20not%20speaking%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20hearing%20the%20conversations%20about%20national%20abortion%20bans%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20hearing%20conversations%20about%20'Is%20climate%20change%20a%20hoax%3F'%20when%2070%25%20of%20my%20state%20is%20water-lined%20and%20waterlogged%20areas%2C%20and%20we%20see%20the%20impacts%20of%20this%20every%20single%20day.%20So%20they%20just%20weren't%20speaking%20to%20the%20people%20of%20my%20state%2C%20or%20frankly%2C%20I'm%20just%20not%20sure%20who%20they're%20actually%20speaking%20to.%26quot%3B%3Cu%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20that%20Moore%20has%20spoken%20about%20the%20need%20to%20defy%20ideological%20divides%20on%20major%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwes-moore-maryland-governor-economy-guns-book-bans-democrats-military-2023-7%5C%22%3EDuring%20an%20interview%3