22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Farticle%2Fmore-than-1-500-treasures-missing-from-british-museum-hbd3hmzs7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Times.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20missing%20objects%2C%20which%20include%20semi-precious%20gems%20and%20gold%20coins%2C%20were%20kept%20in%20the%20museum's%20basement%20galleries%20and%20were%20not%20on%20public%20display%2C%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%26quot%3Black%20of%20proper%20cataloging%26quot%3B%20made%20it%20possible%20to%20remove%20the%20items%2C%20the%20source%20said.%20The%20museum%20has%20admitted%20that%20many%20artifacts%20in%20its%20collections%20are%20not%20cataloged%2C%20per%20The%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20Museum%20was%20first%20alerted%20that%20several%20missing%20objects%20were%20being%20sold%20online%20years%20ago%2C%20The%20Times%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20museum%20last%20week%20said%20they%20would%20take%20legal%20action%20against%20the%20fired%20employee%20and%20that%20police%20were%20investigating%2C%20per%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Farticle%2Fbritish-museum-worker-sacked-over-missing-items-including-jewellery-lqxbqm2vn%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Times.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fired%20man%2C%20Peter%20Higgs%2C%20who%20worked%20as%20a%20curator%20at%20the%20museum%20for%20over%2030%20years%2C%20has%20denied%20wrongdoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20former%20trustee%20at%20the%20museum%20said%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bpuzzling%26quot%3B%20case%20as%20curators%20typically%20consider%20themselves%20custodians%20of%20the%20artifacts%20they%20work%20with%20and%20would%20not%20steal%20or%20deface%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20added%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bfascinating%20thought%26quot%3B%20that%20kleptomania%20could%20have%20spurned%20the%20thefts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20see%20that%20as%20a%20realistic%20pos