ior%20official%20at%20the%20Federation%20%E2%80%93%20Amit%20Bhatnagar%2C%20General%20Manager%2C%20TRIFED%20%E2%80%93%20had%20responded%20to%20TRIFED%20chairman%20Ramsinh%20Rathwa%E2%80%99s%20note%20on%20March%2023%20asking%20him%20and%20other%20officials%20to%20be%20present%20at%20the%20meeting%20by%20saying%20that%20Rathwa%20was%20asking%20for%20the%20cooperative%20staff%E2%80%99s%20presence%20%E2%80%9Cin%20a%20meeting%20of%20organisations%20with%20political%20aspect%E2%80%9D.%20This%2C%20Bhatnagar%20said%2C%20was%20against%20service%20rules%20%E2%80%9Cwhich%2C%20inter-alia%2C%20provide%20that%20every%20government%20servant%20shall%2C%20at%20all%20times%2C%20maintain%20political%20neutrality%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhatnagar%20added%20that%20it%20was%20incumbent%20upon%20officials%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20only%20to%20maintain%20political%20neutrality%20but%E2%80%A6also%20appear%20to%20do%20so%E2%80%A6and%20not%20subscribe%20in%20aid%20of%2C%20or%20assist%20in%20any%20other%20manner%20in%20this%20regard%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20meeting%20took%20place%20on%20March%2028%2C%20according%20to%20the%20newspaper%2C%20only%20Rathwa%20%E2%80%93%20a%20former%20BJP%20MP%20%E2%80%93%20was%20present%20from%20TRIFED.%20Vanvasi%20Kalyan%20Ashram%E2%80%99s%20main%20liaison%20with%20the%20government%2C%20Sharad%20Chavan%2C%20and%20Sahakar%20Bharati%20national%20president%20D.N.%20Thakur%20attended%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minutes%20of%20the%20meeting%20reflected%20discussions%20about%20potential%20collaborations%20between%20TRIFED%20and%20the%20two%20organisations%2C%20both%20of%20which%20are%20described%20as%20NGOs%20engaged%20in%20social%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Chavan%20and%20Thakur%20learnt%20of%20Bhatnagar%E2%80%99s%20description%20of%20their%20organisations%20as%20%E2%80%98political%E2%80%99%20they%20reportedly%20objected%2C%20and%20demanded%20the%20immediate%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20June%2030%2C%20the%20Vanvasi%20Kalyan%20Ashram%20sent%20a%20legal%20notice%20to%20TRIFED%20Managing%20Director%20Gupta%2C%20saying%20it%20had%20been%20%E2%80%9Cwrongly%20presumed%E2%80%9D%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Ca%20political%20organisation%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20demanding%20immediate%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20March%2024%20letter%20by%20Bhatnagar%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%20%E2%80%9COn%20July%2024%2C%20Chavan%20wrote%20to%20Union%20Tribal%20Affairs%20Minister%20Arjun%20Munda%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20TRIFED%20letter%20%E2%80%9Ctarnishes%20our%20nationwide%20image%E2%80%9D%20and%20demanding%20a%20probe%20and%20legal%20action%20against%20the%20persons%20responsible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2022%2C%20Bhatnagar%20reportedly%20wrote%20to%20Rathwa%20and%20said%20his%20earlier%20letter%20%E2%80%9Cseems%20to%20have%20caused%20miscommunication%20and%20should%20be%20withdrawn%20with%20immediate%20effect%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20aforesaid%20letter%20stands%20withdrawn%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Rathwa%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20the%20dispute%20%E2%80%9Cis%20yet%20to%20be%20resolved%E2%80%9D.%20He%20claimed%20the%20%E2%80%9Cwithdrawal%E2%80%9D%20was%20done%20by%20the%20official%20in%20question%20only%20to%20avoid%20legal%20trouble.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693058401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26191219%2Fimages-1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fofficials-at-tribal-affairs-ministry-linked-body-stayed-away-from-meeting-with-rss-affiliates%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20officials%20said%20it%20was%20incumbent%20upon%20them%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20only%20to%20maintain%20political%20neutrality%20but%E2%80%A6also%20appear%20to%20do%20so%E2%80%A6and%20not%20subscribe%20in%20aid%20of%2C%20or%20assist%20in%20any%20other%20manner%20in%20this%20regard%E2%80%9D.%20The%20RSS-linked%20bodies%20have%20since%20objected%20to%20being%20called%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fofficials-at-tribal-affairs-ministry-linked-body-stayed-away-from-meeting-with-rss-affiliates%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIndia%20Leader%20On%20Climate%20Action%2C%20Misleading%20Narratives%20By%20NGOs%26quot%3B%3A%20RK%20Singh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20Power%20Minister%20RK%20Singh%20today%20said%20India%20is%20a%20world%20leader%20in%20energy%20transition%20and%20climate%20action%20and%20the%20narrative%20being%20spread%20by%20%26quot%3Bsome%20NGOs%20in%20the%20developed%20world%26quot%3B%20is%20totally%20misleading.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fspecial.ndtv.com%2Fdecoding-g20-ndtv-conclave-121%2F%5C%22%3ENDTV%20Decoding%20G20%20Conclave%3C%2Fa%3E%20today%2C%20the%20minister%C2%A0said%20the%20NGOs%20will%2C%20for%20example%2C%20say%20that%20India%20is%20a%20huge%20country%20and%20therefore%20its%20total%20emissions%20are%20high.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20ridiculous%2C%20you%20don't%20decide%20on%20the%20emissions%20depending%20on%20the%20size%20of%20the%20country.%20A%20small%20island%20will%20be%20consuming%20huge%20quantities%20of%20energy%20per%20capita%2C%20yet%20its%20total%20emissions%20will%20be%20less.%20You%20have%20to%20talk%20about%20it%20in%20per%20capita%20terms%2C%20like%20you%20talk%20about%20GDP.%20The%20narrative%20has%20to%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Minister%20For%20Power%2C%20New%20and%20Renewable%20Energy%20also%20claimed%20that%20India%20will%20far%20exceed%20its%20promise%20made%20in%20Glasgow%20to%20have%2050%25%20of%20its%20power%20capacity%20from%20non-fossil%20fuel%20sources%20by%202030%20and%20actually%20achieve%20a%20figure%20of%2065%25.%20The%20promise%20was%20made%20at%20the%20COP26%20in%202021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20said%20one%20of%20the%20issues%20with%20renewable%20energy%20is%20that%20storage%20is%20expensive%2C%20and%20the%20developed%20world%20has%20not%20done%20enough%20about%20it.%20He%20said%20that%2C%20in%20a%20bid%20that%20came%20recently%2C%20the%20price%20for%20storage%20came%20to%20Rs%2010%20per%20kilowatt-hour%20(kWh)%20whereas%20the%20renewable%20energy%20cost%20is%20Rs%202.6%20per%20kWh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20you%20get%20one%20unit%20of%20energy%20for%20Rs%202.6%20and%20to%20store%20it%20for%20one%20hour%20you%20need%20to%20pay%20Rs%2010%2C%20so%20the%20total%20cost%20comes%20to%20Rs%2012.6.%20That%20is%20just%20not%20viable%2C%20so%20you%20have%20to%20add%20volume%20for%20storage.%20We%20are%20doing%20that%2C%20but%20if%20the%20developed%20world%20had%20started%20doing%20this%20when%20they%20started%20talking%20about%20the%20climate%2C%20today%20we%20would%20not%20have%20such%20a%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EListing%20India's%20achievements%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%20India%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20country%20whose%20rate%20of%20transition%20to%20renewable%20energy%20is%20one%20of%20the%20fastest%20in%20the%20world%20and%20the%20rate%20of%20renewable%20energy%20capacity%20addition%20is%20the%20fastest%20in%20the%20world.%20All%20this%20was%20done%2C%20he%20said%2C%20while%20making%20sure%20that%20electricity%20is%20available%20for%20the%20country's%20growth.%5Cn%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22NDTV%20G20%20Conclave%20-%20watch%20live%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fspecial.ndtv.com%2Fdecoding-g20-ndtv-conclave-121%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22g20%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fdecoding20-1200x738.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20emerged%20as%20the%20only%20country%20whose%20energy%20transition%20actions%20are%20commensurate%20with%20a%20sub-2-degree%20rise%20in%20global%20temperature.%20In%202017%2C%20interlocutors%20from%20western%20countries%20used%20to%20talk%20to%20me%20about%20how%20necessary%20it%20is%20to%20transition%20and%20how%20India%20should%20be%20doing%20more.%20It%20took%20me%20two%20years%20and%20now%20nobody%20talks%20to%20me%20about%20that%2C%20they%20are%20mostly%20on%20the%20defensive%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20said%20India's%20per%20capita%20emissions%20are%202.19%20tonnes%20per%20year%20and%20the%20world%20average%20is%206.4%20tonnes%20per%20year.%20The%20per%20capita%20emissions%20of%20the%20developed%20world%20are%203%20to%204%20times%20the%20global%20average%2C%20he%20added.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20have%20an%20economy%20that%20is%20growing%20at%207%25%2C%20electricity%20from%20coal%20will%20also%20grow.%20But%20the%20point%20is%20that%20our%20renewable%20energy%20capacity%20is%20growing%20faster.%20The%20narrative%20has%20to%20change.%20We%20will%20meet%20the%20energy%20requirement%20for%20our%20growth%2C%20because%20we%20have%20a%20right%20to%20grow.%20The%20hypocrisy%20of%20developed%20countries%20is%20amazing%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20minister%20asserted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693058280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fiamm8smo_rk-singh-650_650x400_26_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fby-2030-65-of-power-capacity-from-non-fossil-fuel-power-minister-rk-singh-4332017%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Power%20Minister%20RK%20Singh%20today%20said%20India%20is%20a%20world%20leader%20in%20energy%20transition%20and%20climate%20action%20and%20the%20narrative%20being%20spread%20by%20%26quot%3Bsome%20NGOs%20in%20the%20developed%20world%26quot%3B%20is%20totally%20misleading.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news