tball-related%20activities%20at%20national%20and%20international%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20world%20football's%20governing%20body%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20explaining%20it%20would%20last%2090%20days%2C%20pending%20their%20disciplinary%20proceedings.%20Rubiales%20kissed%20Hermoso%20after%20Spain's%20victory%20over%20England%20but%20Hermoso%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20Spanish%20FA%20chief%20did%20not%20have%20her%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20attracted%20criticism%20from%20all%20corners%20of%20the%20world%20with%20the%20footballers'%20union%20Futpro%20saying%20that%2081%20players%20were%20striking%20and%20will%20not%20play%20for%20the%20national%20side%20till%20Rubiales%20was%20removed.%20However%2C%20the%20Spanish%20FA%20chief%20remained%20defiant%20and%20he%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20he%20will%20not%20step%20down%20from%20his%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlayers%20from%20World%20Cup%20runners-up%20England%20released%20a%20statement%20in%20support%20of%20Hermoso%20on%20their%20social%20networks%2C%20signed%20%26quot%3BThe%20Lionesses%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnacceptable%20actions%20allowed%20to%20happen%20by%20a%20sexist%20and%20patriarchal%20organisation.%20Abuse%20is%20abuse%20and%20we%20have%20all%20seen%20the%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20behaviour%20of%20those%20who%20think%20they%20are%20invincible%20must%20not%20be%20tolerated%20and%20people%20shouldn't%20need%20convincing%20to%20take%20action%20against%20any%20form%20of%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20stand%20with%20you%2C%20Jenni%20Hermoso%2C%20and%20all%20players%20of%20the%20Spanish%20team.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20tournament%2015%20Spain%20players%20had%20taken%20a%20similar%20strike%20against%20the%20federation%20and%20coach%20Jorge%20Vilda%2C%20but%20many%20relented%20and%20three%20were%20part%20of%20the%20team's%20triumph%20in%20Australia%20and%20New%20Zealand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20players%2C%20including%20double%20Ballon%20d'Or%20winner%20Alexia%20Putellas%2C%20published%20messages%20of%20support%20for%20Hermoso%20on%20social%20media%20on%20Friday%2C%20some%20including%20the%20phrase%20%26quot%3Bit's%20over%26quot%3B%20--%20potentially%20referring%20to%20Rubiales'%20leadership%20of%20Spanish%20football.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20Putellas%2C%20Hermoso%2C%20player%20of%20the%20tournament%20Aitana%20Bonmati%20and%20many%20more%20say%20they%20will%20not%20play%20for%20Spain%20again%20until%20Rubiales%20and%20potentially%20others%20leave%20their%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20federation%20also%20appeared%20to%20send%20a%20thinly%20veiled%20threat%20to%20the%20striking%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20RFEF%20respects%2C%20as%20it%20has%20always%20respected%2C%20the%20decisions%20of%20the%20players%20who%20wish%20to%20participate%20or%20not%20with%20the%20Spanish%20national%20team%20in%20international%20matches%2C%20although%20it%20is%20clear%20national%20team%20duty%20is%20an%20obligation%20for%20all%20federated%20persons%20if%20they%20are%20called%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20RFEF%20added%20in%20their%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Spanish%20government%20have%20started%20a%20process%20which%20may%20allow%20them%20to%20suspend%20Rubiales%20from%20his%20post%20next%20week%2C%20while%20FIFA%20have%20opened%20a%20disciplinary%20investigation%20into%20his%20behaviour%20at%20the%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20AFP%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693053480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fmj0ojk2_asfaf_625x300_26_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffifa-women-s-world-cup-2023%2Ffifa-suspends-spanish-fa-chief-following-kiss-row-in-womens-world-cup-final-4332081%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22FIFA%20suspended%20Luis%20Rubiales%20as%20president%20of%20Spain's%20football%20federation%20for%20kissing%20Spanish%20Women's%20World%20Cup%20player%20J