3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fniger-coup-uraniu_n_64cd5515e4b01ca15989d8e9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Uranium%20from%20Niger%20helps%20power%20Europe%2C%20but%20all%20eyes%20are%20on%20the%20West%20African%20country%20after%20the%20military%20overthrew%20its%20elected%20president.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A73%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fniger-coup-uraniu_n_64cd5515e4b01ca15989d8e9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-huffpost-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fniger-coup-uraniu_n_64cd5515e4b01ca15989d8e9%2Famp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fniger-coup-uraniu_n_64cd5515e4b01ca15989d8e9%2Famp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDigital%20Connectivity%20Driving%20India's%20Growth%26quot%3B%3A%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20Chief%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20of%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20has%20said%20that%20a%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20why%20India%20has%20seen%20the%20fastest%20growth%20among%20large%20economies%20for%20three%20years%20in%20a%20row%20is%20affordable%20digital%20connectivity%20and%20the%20digital%20ID%2C%20or%20Aadhaar%2C%20that%20has%20been%20issued%20to%20most%20of%20its%201.4%20billion-strong%20population.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorge%20Brende%20was%20speaking%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fspecial.ndtv.com%2Fdecoding-g20-ndtv-conclave-121%2F%5C%22%3ENDTV's%20Decoding%20G20%20Conclave%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20he%20was%20part%20of%20a%20panel%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Voice%20of%20the%20Global%20South%26quot%3B%20with%20NK%20Singh%2C%20co-convener%2C%20G20%20Independent%20Expert%20Group%20on%20Reforms%20in%20Multilateral%20Development%20Banks%20and%20Vera%20Songwe%2C%20chair%20and%20founder%2C%20Liquidity%20and%20Sustainability%20Facility%2C%20Africa%20Growth%20Initiative%2C%20Brookings%20Institution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Brende%20also%20said%20he%20had%20seen%20on%20television%20the%20other%20day%20that%20a%20grandmother%20in%20Assam%20was%20wiring%20money%20to%20her%20grandchildren%20using%20her%20cellphone.%20%26quot%3BWhere%20else%20is%20that%20happening%3F%20If%20India%20is%201.4%20billion%20people%20digitally%20connected%20and%20there%20are%204%20billion%20people%20out%20of%207%20billion%20people%20(in%20the%20world)%20not%20digitally%20connected.%20You%20have%20a%20huge%2C%20huge%20advantage...%20It%20is%20a%20prerequisite%20for%20economic%20growth%20and%20for%20poverty%20eradication%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20WEF%20chief's%20views%20were%20echoed%20by%20Mr%20Singh%20and%20Ms%20Songwe.%20%26quot%3BFinancial%20inclusion%20is%20a%20micro%20and%20macro%20issue.%20If%20you%20are%20not%20financially%20inclusive%2C%20for%20those%20who%20are%20out%20of%20it%2C%20not%20having%20access%20to%20financial%20tools%20is%20a%20terrible%20thing.%20And%20poverty%20is%20a%20terrible%20thing.%20What%20India%20is%20doing%20with%20the%20Aadhaar%20program%20is%20about%20including%20people%20in%20the%20financial%20sector%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Songwe%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20minute%20you%20have%20enough%20information%2C%20people%20become%20part%20of%20the%20formal%20economy.%20We%20can%20bring%20the%20Small%20and%20Medium%20Enterprises%20(SMEs)%20in.%20We%20can%20grow%20them%20faster%20and%20they%20can%20become%20job-creating%20entities.%20And%20that%20is%20why%20you%20are%20the%20fastest%20growing%20economy%20in%20the%20world.%20Because%20your%20Aadhaar%20economy%20is%20now%20paying%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20said%20this%20has%20huge%20implications%20for%20empowering%20people%20who%20are%20outside%20the%20digital%20framework.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20a%20macro-economic%20perspective%2C%20digital%20access%20is%20also%20a%20growth%20disruptor.%20People%20are%20concerned%20with%20the%20enigma%2C%20that%20given%20a%20lot%20of%20other%20disabilities%2C%20how%20is%20it%20that%20India%20is%20the%20fastest%20growing%20economy%3F%20This%20is%20because%20economic%20models%20do%20not%20work%20if%20you%20introduce%20a%20disrupting%20factor.%20That%20disrupting%20factor%20is%20technology%20with%20a%20medium%20of%20digital%20access%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20India%20being%20the%20pharmaceutical%20headquarters%20of%20the%20world%2C%20Mr%20Borge%20said%20many%20people%20forget%20that%20the%20country%20is%20%26quot%3Bworld-leading%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20pharmaceutical%20side.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20India%20has%20a%20huge%20opportunity%20to%20go%20from%20manufacturing%20pharmaceutical%20and%20generic%20products%20to%20also%20invest%20and%20be%20the%20developer%20and%20have%20the%20patents%20and%20then%20you%20have%20the%20full%20value%20chain%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20WEF%20chief%20also%20spoke%20about%20climate%20change%20and%20the%20need%20to%20tackle%20it.%20%26quot%3BClimate%20change%20is%20happening%20here%20and%20now%2C%20and%20we%20are%20paying%20a%20price.%20It's%20affecting%20agri%20production.%20We%20are%20not%20seeing%20enough%20action.%20India's%20G20%20presidency%20underlines%20the%20need%20for%20faster%20decarbonisation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%5Cn%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22NDTV%20G20%20Conclave%20-%20watch%20live%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fspecial.ndtv.com%2Fdecoding-g20-ndtv-conclave-121%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22g20%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fdecoding20-1200x738.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20said%20the%20financing%20of%20the%20orderly%20transition%20to%20green%20energy%20remains%20an%20enigma%20and%20is%20a%20challenge%20that%20is%20being%20worked%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Songwe%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20electric%20vehicle%20industry%20in%20India%20witnessing%20a%20boom%20and%20the%20reskilling%20that%20this%20and%20the%20new%20climate%20economy%20would%20necessitate.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20take%20people%20from%20collecting%20data%20to%20data%20centres%20and%20artificial%20intelligence.%20We%20are%20going%20to%20move%20people%20from%20fixing%20cars%20to%20being%20technologists%20that%20actually%20make%20sure%20you%20can%20drive%20a%20Tesla.%20This%20is%20a%20whole%20reskilling%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20startups%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20continue%20to%20see%20India%20to%20be%20not%20only%20the%20prime-mover%2C%20a%20catalytic%2C%20but%20an%20important%20destination%20for%20startups.%20Technology%20is%20an%20enabler%20but%20also%20a%20disruptor.%20I%20think%20that%20we%20are%20undergoing%20a%20period%20of%20readjustment%20of%20startups%20with%20newer%20technology%20on%20the%20horizon%20and%20newer%20challenges%20on%20the%20horizon...%20I%20see%20that%20the%20vibrancy%20which%20we%20talked%20about%20in%20startups%20will%20come%20back%20to%20this%20country%20with%20even%20greater%20force.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693050900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fak0b1jvg_ndtv-panel-conclave-borge-brende-650_625x300_26_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faffordable-digital-connectivity-aadhaar-driving-indias-growth-world-economic-forum-chief-4331967%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20president%20of%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20has%20said%20that%20a%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20why%20India%20has%20seen%20the%20fastest%20growth%20among%20large%20economies%20for%20three%20years%20in%20a%20row%20is%20affordable%20digital%20connectivity%20and%20the%20digital%20ID%2C%20or%20Aadhaar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faffordable-digital-connectivity-aadhaar-driving-indias-growth-world-economic-forum-chief-4331967%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampp