eo%20from%20a%20school%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%2C%20the%20boy%20stands%20helplessly%2C%20tears%20streaming%20down%20his%20face%2C%20while%20the%20teacher%2C%20Tripta%20Tyagi%20-%20she%20is%20also%20the%20principal%20-%20makes%20communal%20remarks%20and%20eggs%20on%20other%20students%20to%20slap%20him%20for%20not%20doing%20his%20homework.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20declared%20it%20-%20all%20Muslim%20children%20should%20be%20beaten%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20the%20principal%20of%20Neha%20Public%20School%20to%20someone%20not%20on%20camera.%20The%20incident%20took%20place%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELoud%20slaps%20are%20heard%20as%20the%20students%20follow%20their%20teacher's%20instruction.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20don't%20you%20hit%20harder%3F%20Whose%20turn%20is%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20says%20in%20the%20wrenching%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boy%20was%20forced%20to%20stand%20for%20hours%2C%20humiliated%20and%20beaten%2C%20his%20father%20told%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20son%20is%20seven.%20The%20teacher%20had%20my%20child%20beaten%20up%20repeatedly%20by%20students.%20My%20nephew%20made%20the%20video%2C%20he%20had%20gone%20to%20school%20for%20some%20work...%20My%20seven-year-old%20was%20tortured%20for%20an%20hour%20or%20two.%20He%20is%20scared.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20Hindu-Muslim%20issue.%20We%20want%20the%20law%20to%20take%20its%20own%20course%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20boy's%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20child%20is%20in%20shock%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20didn't%20report%20the%20crime%20earlier.%20When%20the%20video%20went%20viral%2C%20the%20police%20registered%20a%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20done%20a%20full%20investigation.%20On%20the%20complaint%20of%20the%20child's%20father%2C%20we%20have%20registered%20a%20case%20against%20the%20accused%20teacher%2C%20departmental%20action%20is%20also%20being%20taken%20against%20the%20teacher.%20Counselling%20of%20the%20child%20and%20his%20family%20is%20also%20being%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Arvind%20Mallappa%2C%20District%20Magistrate%2C%20Muzaffarnagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20police%20officer%20claimed%20after%20a%20probe%2C%20they%20had%20established%20that%20the%20teacher%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20mothers%20of%20those%20Muslim%20children%20who%20do%20not%20pay%20attention%20to%20the%20studies%20of%20their%20wards%2C%20their%20academics%20get%20totally%20destroyed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20principal%20sought%20to%20defend%20her%20egregious%20act%20and%20also%20claimed%20the%20video%20was%20edited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20live%20in%20Hindu-Muslim%20harmony.%20Many%20students%20in%20our%20school%20are%20Muslims.%20That%20child%20did%20not%20bring%20his%20homework%20that%20day%2C%20I%20said%20in%20the%20video%20that%20Muhammedan%20mothers%20should%20not%20take%20their%20children%20to%20their%20maternal%20uncle's%20house%20as%20exams%20are%20approaching.%20But%20they%20made%20this%20video%2C%26quot%3B%20Tripta%20Tyagi%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20pressure%20from%20the%20child's%20parents%20to%20be%20strict%20with%20him.%20I%20am%20handicapped%2C%20so%20I%20made%20some%20students%20slap%20him%20up%20so%20that%20he%20would%20start%20doing%20his%20homework%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bminor%20issue%26quot%3B.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BThis%20wasn't%20my%20intention.%20They%20all%20are%20like%20my%20kids%20and%20I%20am%20accepting%20my%20mistake%2C%20but%20this%20was%20unnecessarily%20turned%20into%20a%20big%20issue.%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20politicians%20that%20this%20was%20a%20small%20matter.%20Leaders%20like%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20have%20tweeted%2C%20but%20it%20was%20not%20such%20a%20big%20thing%20to%20tweet%20about.%20How%20will%20teachers%20teach%20if%20daily%20issues%20like%20these%20are%20made%20viral%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20provoked%20a%20pol