hough%20his%20face%20was%20streaked%20with%20tears%2C%20the%20teacher%20taunted%20a%20classmate%20for%20not%20raining%20blows%20hard%20enough%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20boy%20being%20slapped%20was%20Muslim%20and%20that%20the%20teacher%20made%20a%20sweeping%2C%20derogatory%20reference%20to%20Muslims%2C%20only%20added%20to%20the%20horrendous%20nature%20of%C2%A0%20the%20video%20seen%20on%20social%20media%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20public%20outrage%2C%20the%20police%20visited%20the%20school%20in%20Muzzafarnagar%20district%20and%20said%20it%20would%20take%20appropriate%20action.%20Of%20course%2C%20had%20the%20victim%20been%20a%20Hindu%20and%20the%20perpetrator%20a%20Muslim%2C%20the%20teacher%20would%20have%20been%20promptly%20arrested%20and%20their%20home%20bulldozed%20by%20an%20eager%20state%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20the%20boy%E2%80%99s%20father%20was%20too%20scared%20or%20weary%20to%20initiate%20action%20is%20emblematic%20of%20the%20eroding%20trust%20between%20minorities%20and%20the%20legal%20institutions%20responsible%20for%20protecting%20them.%20He%20took%20the%20only%20recourse%20available%20by%20forbidding%20his%20son%20to%20attend%20school.%20Perhaps%20this%20is%20the%20result%20that%20those%20consumed%20with%20the%20bigotry%20of%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%20hoped%20for.%20This%20is%20precisely%20what%20happened%20after%20the%20%E2%80%98hijab%20controversy%E2%80%99%20in%20Karnataka%20that%20led%20to%20many%20Muslim%20families%20discontinuing%20their%20daughters%E2%80%99%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20has%20already%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.onmanorama.com%2Fcareer-and-campus%2Ftop-news%2F2023%2F02%2F15%2Fdrastic-cut-in-central-scholarship-fellowship-funds.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecancelled%20many%20of%20the%20scholarships%20earmarked%20for%20minorities%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20a%20crucial%20step%20in%20the%20path%20to%20their%20empowerment%20%E2%80%93%20but%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20flames%20of%20hatred%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20has%20actively%20fanned%20since%202014%20are%20now%20threatening%20to%20singe%20the%20safe%20sanctuary%20of%20our%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20did%20the%20so-called%20mother%20of%20democracy%20get%20to%20this%20abhorrent%20point%3F%20As%20if%20engineered%20riots%20weren%E2%80%99t%20enough%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20modus%20operandi%20to%20sow%20division%20now%20includes%20propaganda%20through%20movies%20steeped%20in%20disinformation%20and%20demonisation%20of%20Muslims.%20Otherwise%20what%20explains%20a%20slew%20of%20anti-Muslim%20movies%20like%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20files%2C%2072%20Hoorain%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EKerala%20Story%3C%2Fem%3E%20being%20promoted%20by%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20top%20brass%3F%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Files%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20vilified%20all%20Kashmiri%20Muslims%2C%20was%20recently%20awarded%20a%20prestigious%20official%20prize%20for%20%E2%80%98national%20integration%E2%80%99!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20country%20we%20have%20become%2C%20shocking%20incidents%20against%20minorities%20which%20should%20have%20been%20a%20matter%20of%20shame%20for%20everyone%20are%20instead%20being%20glorified%20and%20turned%20into%20symbols%20of%20national%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20as%20we%20approach%20next%20year%E2%80%99s%20general%20election%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20will%20only%20encourage%20such%20incidents%20which%20are%20a%20blot%20on%20the%20collective%20conscious%20of%20a%20nation%20that%20was%20once%20led%20by%20Gandhiji.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENever%20had%20I%20imagined%20that%20the%20poison%20spewed%20by%20BJP%20would%20singe%20even%20children.%20While%20the%20dogged%20determination%20of%20our%20scientists%20ensured%20India%20landed%20successfully%20on%20the%20moon%2C%20our%20vitriolic%20politicians%20are%20hell%20bent%20on%20taking%20us%20back%20to%20the%20dark%20ages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20BJP%20government%E2%80%99s%20abysmal%2010-year%20performance%2C%20it%20is%20obvious%20that%20its%20large%20election%20machinery%20will%20rely%20primarily%20on%20religious%20polarisation%20and%20the%20stoking%20of%20communal%20fires%20in%20the%20run%20up%20to%202024.%20Their%20reliance%20on%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20and%20other%20government%20agencies%20to%20browbeat%20their%20opponents%20may%20not%20be%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20BJPs%20nervousness%20after%20its%20crushing%20defeat%20in%20the%20Karnataka%20elections%2C%20all%20the%20sluice%20gates%20have%20been%20opened%20regardless%20of%20where%20the%20hate%20ends%20up.%20And%20now%20the%20poison%20has%20reached%20our%20schools.%20As%20I%20write%20this%2C%20I%20wonder%20what%20will%20it%20take%20for%20my%20country%20to%20awaken%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMehbooba%20Mufti%20is%20president%20of%20the%20Jammu%20Kashmir%20Peoples%E2%80%99%20Democratic%20Party%20and%20a%20former%20chief%20minister%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693041617000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F02142235%2FIMG_0750-e1643792690720.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthe-bjps-poison-has-now-reached-indias-schools%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22How%20did%20the%20so-called%20'mother%20of%20democracy'%20get%20to%20this%20abhorrent%20point%3F%20What%20will%20it%20take%20for%20my%20country%20to%20awaken%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A139%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthe-bjps-poison-has-now-reached-indias-schools%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Muzaffarnagar%3A%20FIR%20Filed%20Against%20Teacher%20Who%20Made%20Students%20Beat%20Up%20Muslim%20Child%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01155958%2FDAEFC20B-9E9E-4268-B054-A64E9B81.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EAn%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20Tripta%20Tyagi%2C%20the%20school%20teacher%20who%20urged%20students%20to%20hit%20their%20eight-year-old%20Muslim%20classmate%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Muzaffarnagar.%20While%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20on%20August%2024%20morning%2C%20an%20FIR%20under%20Sections%20323%20and%20504%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20was%20filed%20after%20a%20video%20of%20the%20violence%20went%20viral%20and%20created%20outrage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuzaffarnagar%20district%20magistrate%20Aravind%20Mallappa%20Bangari%20said%20an%20enquiry%20was%20conducted%20and%20it%20was%20found%20that%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20at%20Neha%20Public%20School%2C%20a%20private%20school.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20police%20approached%20the%20child%E2%80%99s%20parents%20%5Bon%20Friday%5D%2C%20but%20the%20parents%20did%20not%20want%20to%20complain%20then.%20But%20on%20Saturday%20morning%20they%20came%20to%20the%20police%20station%20and%20made%20a%20complaint%2C%20and%20an%20FIR%20was%20registered%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBenarasiyaa%2Fstatus%2F1695329012854489349%5C%22%3EBangari%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fup-teacher-forces-fellow-students-to-slap-muslim-child-ncpcr-orders-not-to-circulate-video%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20boy%E2%80%99s%20family%20was%20earlier%20hesitant%20to%20approach%20the%20police%20because%20he%20did%20not%20think%20he%20would%20be%20properly%20heard.%20However%2C%20as%20the%20outrage%20on%20social%20media%20grew%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20take%20action%20as%20he%20did%20not%20want%20to%20happening%20to%20other%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20around%209%20am%20on%20August%2024%2C%20the%20child%20was%20reportedly%20subjected%20to%20assault%20by%20other%20students%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20teacher.%20Sources%20close%20to%20the%20child%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ci%3EWire%3C%2Fi%3E%20that%20he%20was%20assaulted%20while%20the%20teacher%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9CMohammedans%20should%20be%20beaten%20up%E2%80%9D.%20In%20the%20video%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20several%20children%20can%20be%20seen%20slapping%20the%20crying%20child%2C%20with%20Tyagi%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20declared%20that%20all%20those%20Mohammadan%20%5Bi.e.%20Muslim%5D%20children%20should%20be%E2%80%A6(inaudible).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20large%20number%20of%20opposition%20leaders%20have%20expressed%20outrage%20over%20the%20incident%2C%20and%20also%20blamed%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20was%20creating%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20hate%20and%20communal%20violence%20that%20is%20leading%20to%20such%20incidents.%20%E2%80%9CSowing%20the%20poison%20of%20discrimination%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20innocent%20children%2C%20turning%20a%20holy%20place%20like%20school%20into%20a%20marketplace%20of%20hatred%20%E2%80%93%20nothing%20worse%20a%20teacher%20can%20do%20for%20the%20country.%20This%20is%20the%20same%20kerosene%20spread%20by%20the%20BJP%20which%20has%20set%20every%20corner%20of%20India%20on%20fire.%20Children%20are%20the%20future%20of%20India%20%E2%80%93%20do%20not%20hate%20them%2C%20we%20all%20have%20to%20teach%20love%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20poison%20of%20the%20divisive%20thinking%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%20has%20spread%20so%20much%20in%20the%20society%20that%20on%20the%20one%20hand%20an%20education%20teacher%2C%20Tripta%20Tyagi%2C%20is%20teaching%20the%20lesson%20of%20religious%20hatred%20since%20childhood%20and%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20security%20personnel%20RPF%20jawan%2C%20Chetan%20Kumar%2C%20is%20killing%20innocent%20people%20in%20the%20name%20of%20religion%2C%E2%80%9D%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAIMIM%20leader%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20also%20questioned%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Protection%20of%20Child%20Rights%20and%20its%20chief%20Priyank%20Kangoo.%20As%20a%20first%20response%2C%20Kangoo%20had%20insisted%20that%20videos%20of%20the%20incident%20be%20removed%20from%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20video%20from%20Muzaffarnagar%20where%20a%20teacher%20is%20asking%20her%20students%20to%20slap%20a%20Muslim%20boy%20is%20a%20product%20of%20the%20last%209%20years.%20The%20message%20being%20drilled%20into%20the%20minds%20of%20little%20children%20is%20that%20one%20can%20beat%20up%20%26amp%3B%20humiliate%20a%20Muslim%20without%20any%20repercussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20father%20of%20the%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20(%40asadowaisi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fasadowaisi%2Fstatus%2F1695295517628968985%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2026%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20after%20the%20FIR%20had%20been%20filed%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Flodge-fir-up-teacher-kids-hit-muslim-student-ncpcr-muzaffarnagar-ssp-8910659%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20the%20NCPCR%20has%20told%20the%20Muzaffarnagar%20SSP%20to%20register%20an%20FIR%20against%20Tyagi%20under%20Section%2017%20(child%20being%20subjected%20to%20physical%20punishment%2Fmental%20harassment)%20of%20the%20RTE%20Act%2C%202009.%20The%20SSP%20was%20also%20told%20to%20submit%20an%20action%20taken%20report%20within%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20however%2C%20appears%20to%20be%20trying%20to%20claim%20that%20this%20was%20not%20