F2019%2F01%2F02191508%2FParchment-bg.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Though%20the%20Union%20government%C2%A0received%20256%20applications%20for%20the%20posts%20of%20information%20commissioners%20in%20the%20Central%20Information%20Commission%20(CIC)%2C%20no%20appointments%20have%20been%20made%20in%20eight%20months%20to%20fill%20up%20vacancies%20in%20the%20statutory%20body%20which%20is%20already%20working%20below%20half%20its%20capacity.%20This%20is%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20all%20the%20incumbent%20commissioners%20are%20set%20to%20demit%20office%20by%20the%20end%20of%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20information%20was%20revealed%20on%20Thursday%2C%20August%2024%2C%20in%20response%20to%20a%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20query%20filed%20by%20Commodore%20(Retired)%20Lokesh%20Batra.%20In%20December%202022%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20and%20Training%20(DoPT)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fnational%2Fgovt-invites-applications-for-information-commissioners-in-cic-news-246971%5C%22%3Easked%3C%2Fa%3E%20eligible%20applicants%20to%20apply%20for%20the%20posts%20of%20information%20commissioners%20(not%20exceeding%20six).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deadline%20for%20application%20was%20January%2012%2C%202023%2C%20by%20which%20time%20the%20DoPT%20received%20256%20applications.%20In%20addition%2C%2012%20persons%20sent%20their%20applications%20after%20the%20deadline%20had%20passed.%20Though%20eight%20months%20have%20passed%20since%20the%20deadline%2C%20no%20appointments%20have%20been%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20Commodore%20Batra%E2%80%99s%20RTI%20query%2C%20the%20DoPT%20gave%20details%20of%20the%20search%20and%20selection%20process%20and%20that%20the%20particulars%20of%20applicants%20were%20tabulated%20by%20it%20and%20sent%20to%20a%20search%20committee%20constituted%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20headed%20by%20the%20cabinet%20secretary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3