oners-at-cic-reveals-rti-reply%2F1729320%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520its%2520response%2520to%2520an%2Ccommissioners%2520(not%2520exceeding%2520six).%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20news%20agency%20PTI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERTI%20activists%20have%20long%20protested%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20attempts%20to%20dilute%20the%20landmark%20transparency%20law.%20The%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Act%2C%20passed%20in%20the%20recently%20concluded%20session%20of%20parliament%2C%20will%20further%20reduce%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20RTI%20Act%2C%20activists%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fregressive-amendments-to-rti-act-ncpri-flags-concerns-over-digital-personal-data-protection-bill%5C%22%3Ehave%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Recently%2C%20years%20of%20information%20stored%20on%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20portal%20for%20RTI%20applications%20%E2%80%9Cdisappeared%E2%80%9D%20suddenly.%20After%20activists%20raised%20an%20alarm%2C%20the%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frti-portal-rtionline-years-of-information-disappears%5C%22%3Eclaimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20website%20is%20%E2%80%9Cunder%20maintenance%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Carchival%20data%20will%20be%20available%20soon%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693038542000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F02191508%2FParchment-bg.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcic-applications-no-new-appointments%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20advertisement%20was%20issued%20to%20fill%20up%20vacancies%20in%20the%20statutory%20body%20eight%20months%20ago.%20The%20Central%20Information%20Commission%20is%20already%20working%20below%20half%20its%20capacity%20and%20all%20the%20incumbent%20commissioners%20are%20set%20to%20demit%20office%20by%20the%20end%20of%20November.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22http