ltimately%20use%20deposit%20capital%20for%20designing%20their%20credit%20instruments%20and%20credit%20creation%20power).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wholesale%20Price%20Index%20(WPI)%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20sharply%20declining%20after%202022%2C%20which%20signals%20a%20deflationary%20spiral%20accentuated%20by%20a%20demand-side%20problem%20affecting%20the%20manufacturing%2Findustrial%20sector.%20Private%20firms%20are%20finding%20less%20reason%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98optimistic%E2%80%99%20(contrary%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20finance%20minister%E2%80%99s%20optimistic%20rhetoric%20on%20%E2%80%98India%20shining%E2%80%99)%20and%20aren%E2%80%99t%20investing%20big%20capital%20towards%20new%20production%20capacity%2C%20when%20the%20foreseeable%20demand%20for%20consumer%20and%20capital%20goods%20isn%E2%80%99t%20picking%20up-as%20expected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20private%20investment%20is%20otherwise%20being%20anchored%20by%20select%20big-capital%20business%20groups%20(like%20the%20conglomerates%20led%20by%20Gautam%20Adani%20to%20Mukesh%20Ambani)%20that%20have%20a%20monopolist%20advantage%20(from%20existing%20wealth%20endowments)%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1043134%2Fwhat-the-rise-and-fall-of-adani-stocks-says-about-the-indian-state-and-private-capital%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efor%20the%20purpose%20of%20acquisition%20of%20%E2%80%98new%20asset%20frontiers%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20for%20business%20expansion%20%E2%80%93%20and%20not%20for%20the%20objective%20of%20%E2%80%98investing%20in%20new%20capacity%20building%20for%20growth%20expansion%E2%80%99.%20It%20reflects%20the%20regressive%20state%20of%20alliance%20seen%20between%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1043134%2Fwhat-the-rise-and-fall-of-adani-stocks-says-about-the-indian-state-and-private-capital%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebig%20capital%20and%20the%20Indian%20state%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(signalling%20the%20rise%20of%20high%20cronyism%20and%20oligarchic%20capitalism).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26122130%2Fimage7.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22719%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26122130%2Fimage7.png%20719w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26122130%2Fimage7-300x143.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-669970%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22343%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20Trading%20Economics%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20trade%2C%20exports%20have%20risen%20but%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20imports.%20The%20current%20account%20to%20GDP%20levels%20worsened%20to%20what%20they%20were%20prior%20to%202014%20(before%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power).%20This%20reflects%20a%20failure%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20industrial%20and%20trade%20policy%20to%20pivot%20towards%20areas%20where%20it%20was%20competitive%20and%20had%20a%20comparative%20advantage.%20This%20author%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-exports-can-the-govt-prioritise-service-industry-to-bolster-trade%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20repeatedly%20argued%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20the%20potential%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20rapidly%20growing%20service%20sector%20to%20not%20only%20contribute%20more%20to%20exports%20but%20also%20to%20jobs%20and%20overall%20growth.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C