ng%20in%20worse%20federal%20intrusions.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20is%20happening%20now%20is%20a%20multi-level%20operation%20designed%20to%20harass%20and%20tire%20out%20the%20opposition%20governments%20and%20thus%20make%20them%20unpopular.%20It%20is%20a%20calculated%20federal%20trespass%20aimed%20at%20simultaneously%20stretching%20the%20long%20arm%20of%20duopoly%20to%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20interiors.%20Success%20of%20the%20Delhi%20model%20%E2%80%93%20which%20was%20so%20ruthlessly%20enforced%20to%20strangulate%20the%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20government%20and%20paralyse%20the%20administration%20%E2%80%93%20has%20emboldened%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20extend%20the%20experiment%20to%20other%20opposition-ruled%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20two%20years%2C%20the%20governors%20have%20been%20encouraged%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-lg-directs-chief-secretary-to-recover-rs-97-crore-from-aap-for-political-advertisements%5C%22%3Ebehave%20like%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20V.K.%20Saxena%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Fear%20of%20judicial%20spats%20alone%20acted%20as%20a%20restraint.%20Other%20instruments%20of%20harassment%20are%20fiscal%20arm%20twisting%2C%20misuse%20of%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20welfare%20programmes%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenglish.mathrubhumi.com%2Fnews%2Fkerala%2Fkerala-expresses-concern-over-centre-s-move-to-shift-libraries-to-concurrent-list-1.8799290%5C%22%3Eintrusion%20into%20the%20Concurrent%20List%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20directly%20reach%20out%20to%20voting%20public.%20The%20range%20and%20intensity%20of%20the%20impingement%20into%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20preserves%20is%20mind%20boggling.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20cover%20areas%20like%20agriculture%2C%20education%2C%20cooperatives%2C%20water%2C%20public%20health%2C%20libraries%20and%20sports.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuch%20of%20it%20is%20being%20done%20b