ms%20and%20foundational%20curriculum.%20Both%20are%20interconnected%20to%20each%20other%20in%20a%20symbiotic%20relationship%20of%20strength%20and%20fragility.%20Progressive%20education%20must%20be%20a%20quest%20for%20self-actualisation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStructural%20reform%20of%20equity-focused%20curricular%20decisions%20can%20no%20longer%20ignore%20the%20links%20between%20students%E2%80%99%20achievements%20and%20their%20diverse%20and%20unequal%20socio-economic%20backgrounds.%20Thus%2C%20a%20resilient%20education%20system%20has%20to%20foster%20a%20learning%20environment%20that%20enables%20affective%20skills%2C%20critical%20thinking%20and%20innovation.%20Herein%20lies%20the%20need%20for%20constructive%20engagement%20with%20the%20pedagogy%20of%20gender%20performance%20that%20will%20prepare%20children%20to%20be%20democratic%20citizens.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPedagogy%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20constituent%20element%20of%20curricular%20development%20is%20pedagogy.%20It%20is%20a%20%E2%80%98complex%20philosophy%2C%20politics%20and%20practice%20of%20education%20that%20bears%20an%20ethical%20and%20political%20commitment%20to%20transforming%20oppressive%20social%20conditions.%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20gendered%20pedagogy%20should%20essentially%20be%20%E2%80%98humanising%E2%80%99%20and%20build%20on%20the%20richness%20of%20a%20teacher-student%20relationship.%20Learning%20social%20responsibility%20and%20political%20agency%20are%20informed%20choices%20from%20such%20a%20philosophical%20standpoint.%20Locating%20learning%20in%20social%2Fgender%20issues%20and%20connecting%20with%20shared%20experiences%20and%20confessions%20in%20classroom%20spaces%20are%20fruitful%20takeaways%20for%20collective%20progress.%20Unless%20voices%20are%20unsilenced%2C%20shame%20will%20not%20allow%20children%20to%20talk%20about%20how%20being%20a%20woman%20on%20the%20street%20at%20night%20feels%20or%20how%20technology%20is%20misused%20for%20online%20harassment%20of%20girls.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKnowledge%20production%20and%20its%20claims%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20central%20methodological%20question%20for%20curriculum%20development%20would%20be%20how%20and%20where%20would%20gender%20find%20a%20place.%20My%20answer%20would%20be%20everywhere%3A%20in%20textbook%20chapters%20and%20playrooms.%20Teaching%20is%20a%20performative%20act%20that%20has%20to%20be%20embedded%20in%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20plan-act-observe-reflect%20framework.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20question%20values%20and%20normative%20assumptions%20in%20disciplines%20that%20reinforce%20patterns%20of%20subordination.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20unrecognised%20influence%20of%20gender%20on%20the%20production%20of%20dominant%20knowledge%20and%20existing%20knowledge%20claims%20needs%20nuanced%20classroom%20discussions.%20For%20example%2C%20exploring%20if%20there%20can%20be%20a%20naturally%20sexed%20body%20will%20enable%20an%20engagement%20with%20concerns%20of%20sexuality%2C%20problems%20of%20heteronormativity%2C%20consent%20and%20laws.%20In%20a%20science%20class%2C%20teachers%20could%20discuss%20gendered%20patterns%20in%20scientific%20imagery%20that%20may%20not%20be%20accurate.%20An%20example%20could%20be%20the%20use%20of%20gendered%20metaphors%20in%20human%20reproduction%20that%20presents%20the%20female%20body%20as%20passive.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F12130232%2FJagseer_S_Sidhu_teaching_school_students_about_Wikipedia.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F12130