t%20helped%20me%20see%20beyond%20this%20incident%20and%20move%20forward%20with%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevanshi%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20have%20a%20centre%20in%20Bareilly%20where%20we%20give%20free%20education%20to%20girls.%20It%20started%20off%20with%2015%20girls%2C%20but%20now%20we%20have%20around%20500%20girls%20studying%20with%20us.%20Besides%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311913%2Fassam-teacher-uttam-teron-educates-underprivileged-rural-children-for-free-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebasic%20education%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewe%20also%20give%20them%20computer%20courses%2C%20etc.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98This%20fight%20is%20personal%20to%20me%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%20work%2C%20Devanshi%20met%20a%20child%20with%20hearing%20and%20speech%20impairment.%20%E2%80%9CI%20arranged%20funds%20to%20provide%20her%20with%20a%20cochlear%20implant.%20As%20I%20watched%20her%20get%20better%2C%20I%20experienced%20the%20joy%20of%20motherhood%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20when%20she%20realised%20that%20she%20wanted%20to%20become%20a%20mother%20and%20adopt%20a%20child%20in%20need.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20family%2C%20especially%20my%20grandparents%2C%20were%20quite%20against%20this%20idea.%20They%20were%20concerned%20that%20no%20one%20would%20then%20marry%20me.%20Society%20has%20made%20up%20all%20sorts%20of%20norms%20against%20women%20wishing%20to%20become%20a%20mother%20%5Bin%20unconventional%20ways%5D.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20my%20mother%20who%20supported%20me%20throughout%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20registered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F121433%2Fadoption-stories-india-change-stigma-stereotypes-perception%2F%5C%22%3Ewith%20an%20adoption%20agency.%20%3C%2Fa%3EAnd%20after%20months%20of%20waiting%2C%20I%20finally%20had%20her!%20During%20the%20whole%20process%2C%20I%20would%20sit%20in%20the%20already-ready%20nursery.%20I%E2%80%99d%20sit%20there%20and%20pray%20that%20%E2%80%98Wherever%20my%20baby%20is%2C%20let%20her%20be%20safe%20and%20I%E2%80%99ll%20bring%20her%20home%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Ffeature-image-2-1692973076.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Devanshi%20with%20her%20daughter%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Ffeature-image-2-1692973076.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Ffeature-image-2-1692973076-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Ffeature-image-2-1692973076-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Ffeature-image-2-1692973076-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Ffeature-image-2-1692973076-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-328280%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDevanshi%20with%20her%20daughter.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Devanshi%20Yadav%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2027%2C%20Devanshi%20became%20a%20single%20mother.%20Her%20daughter%20Vanmayi%20came%20into%20her%20life%20when%20the%20child%20was%20only%20six%20months%20old.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20she%20first%20looked%20towards%20me%2C%20my%20whole%20world%20stopped.%20I%20instantly%20fell%20in%20love.%20She%20was%20my%20dream%20come%20true%20%E2%80%94%20she%20made%20me%20stop%20questioning%20why%20bad%20things%20happen%20in%20the%20world.%20She%20eases%20my%20pain%20w