d%20ignite%20his%20life%E2%80%99s%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F971079_518963701499082_1454533731_n-1692182167.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bindeshwar%20Pathak%20provided%20employment%20opportunities%20to%20people%20from%20the%20marginalised%20communities.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F971079_518963701499082_1454533731_n-1692182167.jpg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F971079_518963701499082_1454533731_n-1692182167-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F971079_518963701499082_1454533731_n-1692182167-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F971079_518963701499082_1454533731_n-1692182167-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F971079_518963701499082_1454533731_n-1692182167-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327299%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBindeshwar%20Pathak%20provided%20employment%20opportunities%20to%20people%20from%20marginalised%20communities.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20journey%20of%20empathy%20and%20innovation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPathak%E2%80%99s%20path%20to%20transformation%20was%20paved%20with%20empathy%20and%20innovation.%20Armed%20with%20a%20degree%20in%20sociology%2C%20he%20embarked%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20eradicate%20manual%20scavenging%20and%20uplift%20the%20marginalised.%20His%20groundbreaking%20idea%20of%20a%20two-pit%20pour-flush%20toilet%20not%20only%20eliminated%20the%20need%20for%20manual%20cleaning%20but%20also%20promoted%20safe%20waste%20dispos